s over\ndiscretization elements: material interface preserving and entropy\nconservative. Time integration is performed using SSP Runge-Kutta schemes. The\nhigh-order accuracy, nonlinear stability, and robustness of the present scheme\nare assessed through several numerical experiments in one and two space\ndimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Mar 2022 17:57:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2022 07:53:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-11"}
