n, which are attributed to the unsaturated solid\nsolutions at lower codopant levels and supersaturated solid solutions at higher\nlevels. The present work demonstrates that the Pechini method offers a\nprocessing technique that is superior to sol gel because the former facilitates\nsolid solubility and consequent chemical homogeneity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 07:32:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-23"}
