r activity. Comparisons with\nmagnetograms from the Helioseismic and Magnetic Imager (HMI) demonstrate that\nhigh-activity clusters are located preferentially in the magnetic network and\nabove regions of enhanced magnetic flux density.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 11:23:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
