ied by 50% although the mean value\nof the four model products is close to the observation. This study indicates\nfurther model improvement is necessary to more accurately reproduce the extreme\nconditions. For the model improvement as well as the model evaluation, more\nmeasurements of the high sea states and their wave spectra information are\nwarranted.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2022 13:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-23"}
